OL,3,CLocals push back against energy park
OL,4,Cplans
OL,6,FPlans for an Energy Park near Duns
OL,7,Fhave received pushback from the local
OL,8,Fcommunity.
OL,10,FA group opposing the plans for Lees
OL,11,FHill Energy Park west of Duns held a
OL,12,Fmeeting and called for locals to make
OL,13,Ftheir voices heard during the
OL,14,Fconsultation period.
OL,16,FThe proposal for Lees Hill Energy Park
OL,17,Fby Fred Olsen Renewables includes six
OL,18,Fwind turbines each 200 metres tall,
OL,19,Fsolar panels, and a battery storage
OL,20,Funit.
