OL,6,FThe proposal for the energy park was
OL,7,Fsubmitted by Fred Olsen Renewables to
OL,8,Fthe Scottish Government Energy Consent
OL,9,FUnit earlier this year and is
OL,10,Fcurrently open to consultation and
OL,11,Ffeedback.
OL,13,FCampaigners of Duns Lees Hill Save Our
OL,14,FSkyline (SOS) criticised the height of
OL,15,Fthe turbines at a meeting in Duns on
OL,16,F25 July 2024.
OL,18,FPaul Whitfield said: "We think the 200
OL,19,Fmetre turbines are far too big for
OL,20,Fthis location.
