OL,6,F"You'll see them as far away as well
OL,7,Finto England and Berwick, and we think
OL,8,Fthat this is inappropriate for this
OL,9,Flocation."
OL,11,FAs is standard, Scottish Borders
OL,12,FCouncil is consulted on the proposal
OL,13,Fand takes local feedback into account.
OL,15,FJohn Campbell also spoke at the
OL,16,Fmeeting and said: "We've decided to
OL,17,Ftake matters into our own hands.
