OL,6,F"This is an information meeting, this
OL,7,Fis to inform people. We hope that the
OL,8,Fproduct of this meeting will be sent
OL,9,Fto Scottish Borders Council who will
OL,10,Ftake account of it when they write
OL,11,Ftheir report for the Energy Consent
OL,12,FUnit."
OL,14,FIn a statement, Fred Olsen Renewables
OL,15,Fsaid: "We have been working with
OL,16,Fstakeholders and local residents since
OL,17,F2022 to develop our proposals for Lees
OL,18,FHill Renewable Energy Park.
